Lima is an application for the ATmega328P mpu.

It manages an OLED display and is connected to other mpus via the TWI.
There is no HC-05 serial interface. Twiboot is used for reprogramming.

To build and install the application :-

  $ make
  $ cd ../bali
  $ avril lima

To build and install the application and bootloader :-

  connect the ICSP cable between bali and lima

  $ make image
  $ cd ../bali
  $ (. ./defs.sh && cd ../lima && make avp)

